Some notes now that I've almost finished watching all the files in this torrent.

Video source: looks like PDTV broadcast.
Video: 6.5/10 (a little less than I'd have liked, but tolerable)
Audio: 9/10, WITH an important caveat.

The sound cuts out before the end of two episodes: s02e18 and s02e20. With e18, it's only the last 10 secs, but with e20 it's almost 1 and half minutes.

And in both cases, they're cliffhangers, so it's a real pain.

(I tried playing in both VLC and MPC-HC, same prob in both.)

In the case of e18, the subtitles also finished early; but only one word was missing and I could guess it from context, repeat playing and lipreading :D

In the case of e20, I turned on the subtitles and read them to find out what they were saying.
